# Dashboard Overview

The Power BI dashboard provides an end-to-end view of e-commerce business performance by combining transactional data from a relational database with customer review data from an object store. The dashboard is built using curated tables from the Snowflake ANALYTICS schema.

## Dashboard Objectives

### Objective 1: Sales Performance Analysis

Monitor and analyze sales performance across products, categories, regions, and time periods to identify business trends and growth opportunities.

### Objective 2: Customer Satisfaction Analysis

Measure customer satisfaction using review scores and ratings to understand customer preferences and improve product quality.

---

# Dashboard Page 1: Sales Performance

## Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

* Total Revenue
* Total Orders
* Average Order Value
* Total Customers

## Visualizations

* Monthly Revenue Trend (Line Chart)
* Revenue by Product Category (Bar Chart)
* Revenue by Country or Region (Map Chart)
* Top 10 Products by Sales (Bar Chart)

## Filters and Slicers

* Order Date
* Country
* Product Category

---

# Dashboard Page 2: Customer Satisfaction

## Key Performance Indicators (KPIs)

* Average Review Score
* Total Reviews
* Positive Review Percentage

## Visualizations

* Review Score Trend Over Time (Line Chart)
* Average Rating by Product Category (Bar Chart)
* Top Rated Products (Bar Chart)
* Lowest Rated Products (Bar Chart)

## Filters and Slicers

* Review Date
* Product Category
* Review Score

---

# Data Source

The dashboard integrates data from two sources:

1. Relational database containing customers, orders, products, and order details.
2. Object store containing customer reviews and ratings in CSV or JSON format.

---

# Data Processing Flow

Source Systems → Snowflake RAW Schema → Snowflake STAGING Schema → Snowflake ANALYTICS Schema → Power BI Dashboard

---

# Business Value

* Provides a unified view of sales and customer feedback.
* Enables data-driven decision making.
* Identifies top-performing products and regions.
* Tracks customer satisfaction trends.
* Supports strategic planning and performance monitoring.
